say 'There are '||result||' vertical guides.'
@toc PageStream3:Help/PGS.HEL/MAIN
@endnode

@node GETGUIDE
@remark Document Queries

@{U}@{FG Highlight}GETGUIDE                                                                    @{FG Text}@{UU}

Gets the snap-to-guide settings for a master page
side.

@{B}getguide@{UB} <stem> [MASTERPAGE name]

stem/a       Gets the guide info.
MASTERPAGE/s The master page name. Default=current.

Results:

stem
snap/k       The snap method: ALL|RANGE.
rangeh/d     The horizontal range.
rangev/d     The vertical range.

ARexx Examples:

getguide info
if info.snap='RANGE' then do
   say 'Snap horizontally within '||info.rangeh
   say 'Snap vertically within '||info.rangev
