@node GETMASTERPAGES
@remark Document Queries

@{U}@{FG Highlight}GETMASTERPAGES                                                              @{FG Text}@{UU}

Gets the number of master pages in a document or
chapter and their names.

@{B}getmasterpages@{UB} <stem>
[DOCUMENT name | CHAPTER name]

stem/a      Gets the names of the master pages.
DOCUMENT/s  The document name.
CHAPTER/s   The chapter name.

Results:

The number of master pages in the document or chapter
is returned to RESULT.

stem
0/i         The name of the first master page.
